    "longBusinessSummary": "Duc Long Gia Lai Group JSC, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the electrical components and parts, granite, wood and finished wood products, toll fees BOT, and rental businesses in Vietnam. The company manufactures wooden and other material-based beds, wardrobes, tables, and chairs; manufactures and processes electronic components; and wholesales electronic and telecommunications equipment and components. It is also involved in financial investment; production of electronic equipment; production and processing of granite products; bus station and parking; and mineral exploitation and processing activities. In addition, the company provides hotel and resort; security and bodyguard; villas or apartments for short-term lodging; guesthouses and motels for short-term lodging; road freight transportation; urban, intercity, and interprovincial bus passenger transportation; and road construction services. Further, it leases machinery and equipment, as well as offices; invests in and operates transportation infrastructure under the BOT model; and operates a hydropower plant. Duc Long Gia Lai Group JSC was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Pleiku, Vietnam.",
